Tepco Says Total Amount of Radiation From Fukushima Nuclear Unit Unclear

-- B y   M i c h i o   N a k a y a m a
-- 
2011-04-12T02:44:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/tepco-says-total-amount-of-radiation-from-fukushima-nuclear-unit-unclear.html
The total amount of radiation
released in the crisis at  Japan ’s Fukushima Dai-Ichi nuclear
plant is unclear, Junichi Matsumoto, a spokesman for Tokyo
Electric Power Co., told reporters today.  The nation’s nuclear safety agency said today it raised the
severity rating for the accident to 7, the highest level, citing
the amount of radiation leaked.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michio Nakayama in Tokyo at 
